high_descs: Pick up the soapbar off of the toilet.
walk towards the floorlamp in the living room.
Put the bar next to the floorlamp to turn the light on.
anns.task_desc: Pick up SoapBar and turn FloorLamp on

high_descs: Turn left, go through the doorway by the tv into the hall, go to near the end of the hall, turn left and go through the second to last doorway into the bathroom with a toilet.
Pick up the soapbar off the toilet.
Go out the bathroom door, turn left, and walk to the floorlamp.
anns.task_desc: Get SoapBar off of the toilet and turn on the FloorLamp in the hallway.

high_descs: Cross to the left. Go to the wall. Turn left. Go ahead, turn right. Go to the end and turn left at the second entrance. Go into the bathroom, get to the toilet, turn left move, turn left.
Cross to the left, go forward and then to the right. Exit the bathroom. Turn left. Approach the floorlamp. Pull up the bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: Find a SoapBar. Light a FloorLamp.
